---

<Layout>
  <HeadersBanner HeadersBanners={HeaderBannerData} />
  <UmmahCharity />
  <div class="mt-12">
    <p class="text-maroon text-xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center">
      Morocco Earthquake Appeal
    </p>
    <p
      class="text-sm md:text-xl text-customBeige font-medium text-center mt-5 px-2 md:px-60"
    >
      The Most Catastrophic Earthquake in a Century
    </p>
    <p class="text-grey text-sm md:text-lg font-medium text-center mt-5 px-2 md:px-52">
      A disastrous earthquake struck Morocco on Friday night, September 8th, at
      just past 11 PM local time resulting in a tragic death toll. The casualty
      count is nearing <strong> 3,000,</strong> and over <strong>
        5,600 individuals</strong
      > left injured. According to the details, the epicenter of this earthquake
      of magnitude 6.8 was in the High Atlas Mountains, approximately <strong
        >72 kilometers southwest of Marrakech.</strong
      >
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-10 mb-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div
        class="max-w-80 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden relative"
      >
